<H3> <TI>   Rugova Urges UN To Decide on Protection </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  AU1501205594 Tirana TVSH Television Network in Albanian 1900 
GMT 15 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU1501205594 </F>
<F P=104>  Tirana TVSH Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Albanian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] In an interview given to Prishtina's weekly ZERI, 
commenting on his latest tour of several European countries, 
Ibrahim Rugova, president of the republic of Kosova, states that 
he encountered understanding for the right to independence and 
neutrality of the people of Kosova in all of his meetings. The 
proposal to place Kosova under international protection is 
simply a political means toward Kosova's independence. The UN 
should decide on this with the mediation of the European Union 
and the United States, said Mr. Rugova, among other things, to 
Prishtina's ZERI. 

</TEXT>

