GMT 14 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU1401213794 </F>
<F P=104>  Tirana TVSH Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Albanian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] In a statement, the Democratic Youth Forum, the 
Albanian Students Independent Union, the student wing of the 
Albanian Democratic Party, and the Political Persecutees Youth 
League express their deep indignation and strong protest against 
the Serbian occupying authorities in Prishtina who, 
provocatively and intentionally, have arrested the chairman of 
the Independent Students Union of Prishtina University, Fisnik 
Cukaj. 
  They appeal to all European youth bodies to raise their 
voices to defend their Kosovar counterparts and exert pressure 
so that Fisnik Cukaj and others are not murdered by the Serbian 
dictatorship but can enjoy the legitimate right of European 
citizens. 

