<H3> <TI>   Government Adopts `Text' of Pact With Croatia </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD1901174094 Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service in 
Serbo-Croatian 1418 GMT 19 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1901174094 </F>
