Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Bucharest, ROMPRES, 19/1/1994 -- "Above all, this 
visit has demonstrated Romania's interest in expanding the 
relations with China. Second, it is important in the field of 
direct economic relations, of exchanges", stated State Minister 
Mircea Cosea, president of the Council on Economic Coordination, 
Strategy and Reform, on his return on January 19 from a visit to 
