big economic achievements, the fantastic dynamics of the 
southern zones of China and have established the coordinates of 
relations of collaboration not only in the domain of reform but 
also as regards the revigoration of economic exchanges" Cosea 
added. 
  Expressing satisfaction at the results of the visit, he also 
assessed it has demonstrated both parties' wish "to further the 
traditional Romanian-Chinese relations also in the new 
conditions the two countries are achieving now in the economic 
and social life." 

