Commission, which discussed economic and technical issues 
related to bilateral cooperation, the Greek government 
delegation conducted other business talks today. 
  Talks began at the Agriculture and Food Industry, where Mr. 
Papandoniou was received by Agriculture and Food Minister Halili. 
  The Greek economic delegation held talks with Ministers 
Bitincka [transportation] and Dishnica [finance] and with Deputy 
